{"id": 663, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得上知乎的都是什么样的人？", "description": "整天上知乎到底是一种什么样的体验？", "record_count": 10773, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130105hASBkrfdNT2a73bO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-26T11:31:42Z", "options": [{"id": 28928, "content": "中国最大真人RPG交流社区，中国最急需止泻药之地，真正可以锻炼装X技艺的地方。可是就在几年前，它还是中国最靠谱知识分享地啊…", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199910}, {"id": 28929, "content": "想涨姿势的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327827}, {"id": 30209, "content": "半瓶不满半瓶摇的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301544}, {"id": 28930, "content": "自认为高逼格的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219212}, {"id": 28931, "content": "软广告和有内涵的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299872}, {"id": 29699, "content": "知乎是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169512}, {"id": 31747, "content": "什么人都有吧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340271}, {"id": 28932, "content": "强调“谢邀”的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215823}, {"id": 34564, "content": "我们上的是同一个知乎么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 359599}, {"id": 28934, "content": "逼格略高的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327841}, {"id": 28936, "content": "炫耀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154822}, {"id": 28937, "content": "抖机灵的票数奇高", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154822}, {"id": 30217, "content": "文爱特好，特闲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334111}, {"id": 28938, "content": "不牛逼瞎装逼骗傻逼的人和傻逼的人和牛逼爱看笑话的人和学习装逼的傻逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect